##################
### PROTONMAIL ###
##################

IMAPAccount protonmail
Host 127.0.0.1
Port 1143
User xxx
PassCmd "gpg2 -q --for-your-eyes-only --no-tty -d /home/redplateaus/.config/mutt/protonmail/creds.gpg"
SSLType NONE

IMAPStore protonmail-remote
Account protonmail

MaildirStore protonmail-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path /media/redplateaus/ExtraDrive1/mail/protonmail/
Inbox /media/redplateaus/ExtraDrive1/mail/protonmail/Inbox

Channel protonmail
Master :protonmail-remote:
Slave :protonmail-local:
Patterns * !"Drafts" !"All Mail"
Create Both
SyncState *
